#### What is the expected behavior?

If the value of the model is changed inside selectionChange event, due to an internal validation, it should be updated in the mat-select view.

#### What is the current behavior?

Keeps the selected value.

#### What are the steps to reproduce?

https://stackblitz.com/edit/angular-qa4txi

Select 'invoice' wich is "not allowed". The model is updated to 'note', but mat-select still displays 'invoice'

